&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;ms-outlook-mobile-reference-message&quot;&gt;Space is a warfighting domain. True Anomaly seeks those with the talent and ambition to build the technology that secures it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;ms-outlook-mobile-reference-message&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;OUR MISSION&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;ms-outlook-mobile-reference-message&quot;&gt;True Anomaly delivers decisive capabilities for space superiority. We build autonomous spacecraft, advanced payloads, mission software, and space-based interceptors — enabling the U.S. and its Allies to secure the space environment and counter threats from the ultimate high ground.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;ms-outlook-mobile-reference-message&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;OUR VALUES&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;ms-outlook-mobile-reference-message&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Be the offset.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;We create asymmetric advantages with creativity and ingenuity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;ms-outlook-mobile-reference-message&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What would it take?&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;We challenge assumptions to deliver ambitious results.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;ms-outlook-mobile-reference-message&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;It’s the people.&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Our team is our competitive advantage and we are better together.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;u&gt;YOUR MISSION&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a skilled and detail-oriented &lt;strong&gt;Accounting &amp;amp; Finance Systems Administrator&lt;/strong&gt; to own, manage, and optimize our financial technology stack. This role sits at the intersection of accounting, finance, and technology — serving as the primary administrator and subject matter expert for NetSuite and the broader ecosystem of tools that support our finance organization. You will partner closely with Accounting, Finance, Operations, and IT to ensure our systems are controlled, integrated, and running at peak performance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;RESPONSIBILITIES&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the primary NetSuite Administrator, owning system configuration, user access, roles and permissions, workflows, saved searches, reports, and dashboards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Optimize NetSuite Inventory and Item management, including item setup, inventory transactions, costing methods, and related workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support and maintain integrations between NetSuite and third-party platforms, troubleshooting data flow issues and partnering with vendors or internal teams on enhancements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Administer and support connected finance and accounting tools including procurement, expense, travel, and financial planning platforms.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Accounting and Finance stakeholders to gather requirements, translate business needs into system solutions, and deliver enhancements through the NetSuite development lifecycle (customizations, scripts, workflows, and saved searches).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own system-level internal controls (access controls, segregation of duties, and audit trails) and maintain supporting documentation to ensure audit readiness and policy compliance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain system documentation including process maps, configuration guides, integration specs, and user training materials.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead or support NetSuite upgrades, sandbox testing, and release management.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify opportunities to improve system efficiency, data accuracy, and process automation across the finance tech stack.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide end-user training and support for finance system tools.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;QUALIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;ms-outlook-mobile-reference-message&quot;&gt;Space is a warfighting domain. True Anomaly seeks those with the talent and ambition to build the technology that secures it.&lt;/p&gt;
